 /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.guijj.com/c/117_3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.guijj.com%2Fc%2F117_3.gif&h=a903ad1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"674818412aa9e2a833de6899fbeff7c70758125a","tid":1274130,"uid":38456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4c983eefe6947bc0d88b820db513af0e0e6c54","tid":1274130,"uid":93752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:16:52.000Z","msg":"我都頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb92579ff7fac752cf0e95fbaa7fd44138f917a","tid":1274130,"uid":132461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"(1) imagine you are dead so you are one of them, or you are the ghost instead of the human victims.<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n(2) imagine you are so powerful that you should not fear ghosts but ghosts should fear you<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n(3) understand that most ghosts actually don't do anything when they come out<br />\n<br />\nUsually horror movies only show a brief image of the ghost, then comes a long time of victims' screaming and showing a twisted face. Eventually the victims will die. But the process of how ghosts attack victims is completely skipped.  <br />\n<br />\nIt is the screaming and twisted face that make you feel it must be very scary. Kind of like nervousness, fear is infectious. <br />\n<br />\n========================<br />\n<br />\nI had the same fear in the past. I used the above tips and kept watching some horror movies for training. Now I have got over this fear. Hopefully my suggestions can be of some help to you."},{"pid":"3f66f71c68f7ebb75edd26ec1a5619c85b5a58ac","tid":1274130,"uid":89132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"登記左選民先好睇鬼片"},{"pid":"1b05acd2cfb50c5ae79913dd70e417a62ee56684","tid":1274130,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb92579ff7fac752cf0e95fbaa7fd44138f917a","tid":1274130,"uid":132461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"(1) imagine you are dead so you are one of them, or you are the ghost instead of the human victims.<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n(2) imagine you are so powerful that you should not fear ghosts but ghosts should fear you<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n(3) understand that most ghosts actually don't do anything when they come out<br />\n<br />\nUsually horror movies only show a brief image of the ghost, then comes a long time of victims' screaming and showing a twisted face. Eventually the victims will die. But the process of how ghosts attack victims is completely skipped.  <br />\n<br />\nIt is the screaming and twisted face that make you feel it must be very scary. Kind of like nervousness, fear is infectious. <br />\n<br />\n========================<br />\n<br />\nI had the same fear in the past. I used the above tips and kept watching some horror movies for training. Now I have got over this fear. Hopefully my suggestions can be of some help to you."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:40:21.000Z","msg":"the movies that i watched for training<br />\n<br />\n大頭怪嬰, 童眼, Mama"},{"pid":"c6ec7e7d4e2a286983edbdb5e64896ba03de1d26","tid":1274130,"uid":271718,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"唔怕睇心寒懸疑類既鬼片 但好憎睇jump scare<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c119fa5d9141c90e4eea4238160ef8a4760899c","tid":1274130,"uid":152254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"發多啲夢 對住班狗堆武器真係可以訓練膽量"},{"pid":"ed6d1a2a70cbb61a0de0c2c699bcf0046e59b03a","tid":1274130,"uid":27616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:58:21.000Z","msg":"睇多啲就麻木㗎啦"},{"pid":"0cb733ffac2783b5b8a